					<description><![CDATA[<p>The way people discover businesses is changing fast. With AI tools like ChatGPT influencing buying decisions, visibility isn’t just about Google anymore — it’s about being part of the conversation. This guide from 1111 Media Group explains how to get your business recommended by ChatGPT, earn trust through content and credibility, and stay ahead of competitors in the AI-driven search era.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://1111mediagroup.com/2025/11/19/geo-vs-seo-how-ai-is-transforming-search-marketing-strategies/">GEO vs. SEO: How AI Is Transforming Search Marketing Strategies</a> first appeared on <a href="https://1111mediagroup.com">1111 Media Group</a>.</p>]]></description>
